headline.main: VON PAPEN PRESSES FOR TURKISH ACCORD; Sees Minister on Trade Pact -- Axis Circles Hopeful

lead_paragraph: ANKARA, Turkey, Sept. 29 -- German Ambassador Franz von Papen conferred for an hour and fifteen minutes this afternoon with Turkish Foreign Minister Shukru Saracoglu, the Foreign Affairs Under-Secretary, and Dr. Karl Clodius, the chief of Germany's trade mission to Ankara.
abstract: von Papen conf with Saracoglu and Clodius; U S and Brit Ambs conf; conflicting repts on progress
